name: Puns
jokes: I used to be a baker, but I couldn't make enough dough.
The baker couldn't make enough bread, so he got a new knead assistant.
I'm reading a book on anti-gravity. It's impossible to put down.
I used to play piano by ear, but now I use my hands.
I couldn't figure out how to put my seatbelt on. Then it 'clicked.'
I'm friends with all electricians because we have good current connections.

I'm a fungi, but I'm not a mushroom. I'm a fun guy!

name: Knock-Knock
jokes: Knock, knock. Who's there? Boo. Boo who? Don't cry; it's just a joke!
Knock, knock. Who's there? Lettuce. Lettuce who? Lettuce in; it's cold out here!
Knock, knock. Who's there? Cow says. Cow says who? No, silly, Cow says mooo!
Knock, knock. Who's there? Atch. Atch who? Bless you!
Knock, knock. Who's there? Alpaca. Alpaca who? Alpaca the suitcase; you load up the car!
Knock, knock. Who's there? Hatch. Hatch who? Bless you! Are you sick?
Knock, knock. Who's there? Ben. Ben who? Ben waiting for you all day!
Knock, knock. Who's there? Honeydew. Honeydew who? Honeydew you know how much I love you?
Knock, knock. Who's there? Harry. Harry who? Harry up and answer the door!
Knock, knock. Who's there? Lettuce. Lettuce who? Lettuce in; it's cold out here!

name: Animal Jokes
jokes: Why did the squirrel bring a suitcase to the tree? Because it wanted to pack its acorns!
What do you call a fish with no eyes? Fsh!
How do you catch a squirrel? Climb a tree and act like a nut!
What do you call a bear with no teeth? A gummy bear!
Why don't seagulls fly over the bay? Because then they'd be bagels!
What's a frog's favorite candy? Lollihops!
What do you call a dinosaur with an extensive vocabulary? A thesaurus!
Why did the cat sit next to the computer? It wanted to keep an eye on the mouse!
What do you get when you cross a snowman and a dog? Frostbite!
Why did the cow go to space? It wanted to see the moooon!

name: Science Jokes
jokes: Why do biologists look forward to casual Fridays? They're allowed to wear genes to work!

Why do engineers get stressed? Because they have too many problems to solve!
What did the biologist wear to impress the biologist of their dreams? Designer genes!
